pandoc 
  to: revealjs
  from: markdown-auto_identifiers
  output-file: index.html
  standalone: true
  wrap: none
  default-image-extension: png
  html-math-method:
    method: mathjax
    url: >-
      https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/mathjax/2.7.0/MathJax.js?config=TeX-AMS_HTML-full
  slide-level: 2
  
metadata
  link-citations: true
  width: 1024
  height: 768
  margin: 0.1
  center: false
  navigationMode: linear
  controlsLayout: edges
  controlsTutorial: false
  hash: true
  history: true
  hashOneBasedIndex: true
  fragmentInURL: false
  transition: slide
  backgroundTransition: none
  pdfSeparateFragments: false
  lang: en
  auto-stretch: true
  linestretch: 1.5
  theme:
    - theme/ppt-theme.scss
  transitionSpeed: fast
  slideNumber: c/t
  logo: ''
  code-copy: true
  center-title-slide: false
  chalkboard:
    buttons: false
  touch: true
  controls: true
  hash-type: number
  slide-tone: false
